    <Label name="lblWarning" id="d58e2693-8356-4d0c-8cc1-f28d9e6ff7f9">
        <caption>To load the test data you must know where to get the appropriate data. The data returned will be loaded into the worksheet you specified in Step 1. The application specific data will be placed row by row into the worksheet. You will then be able to modify the workbook to process the loaded data and test the workbook display. Note that when the workbook is saved in Step 6, the worksheet is cleared of all data and functions. Do not include any permanent functions in the worksheet.</caption>
